folder: [View of East River pier and portions of Triborough and Hell Gate Bridges.], Manhattan, NY
text:
East River, showing the pier at the foot of East 91st Street, off York Ave. Also shown (left background) are portions of the Triborough and Hell Gate Bridges.

September 23, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
title: East River - [View of East River pier and portions of Triborough and Hell Gate Bridges.]
